[{"id":"ec2a332475df0749e51ddf1092bfe03b","from":"J. Epstein","from_email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to":"Catherine PARPET","to_list":[{"name":"Catherine PARPET","email":"CPARPET@DARROISVILLEY.COM"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Re:","date":"2007-02-13T18:05:21.000Z","formatted_date":"Feb 13, 2007","formatted_time":"6:05 PM","body":"I have not receivd any documents \n\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: Catherine PARPET <CPARPET@DARROISVILLEY.COM>\nTo: jeeproject@yahoo.com\nCc: Matthieu DE BOISSESON <MDEBOISSESON@DARROISVILLEY.COM>\nSent: Tuesday, February 13, 2007 3:21:37 AM\nSubject: \n\n\nDear Jeffrey,\n \nWe had a meeting this morning with the notary and Mr. Degroux, Juan Pablo Molyneux\u2019 lawyer. I suggest that you send at your earliest convenience the \u201cconfirmation agreement\u201d the draft of which you have received from Ma\u00eetre Chardon. We have tomorrow afternoon a meeting with the sellers\u2019 lawyer and notary. It is necessary that we have this document signed by you at the meeting.\n \nKind regards,\n \nMatthieu de BOISS\u00c9SON\n\n\n \n____________________________________________________________________________________\nDo you Yahoo!?\nEveryone is raving about the all-new Yahoo! Mail beta.\nhttp://new.mail.yahoo.com","body_html":"<html><head><style type=\"text/css\"><!-- DIV {margin:0px;} --></style></head><body><div style=\"font-family:times new roman, new york, times, serif;font-size:12pt\"><DIV style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif\">I have not receivd any documents <BR><BR>\n<DIV style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif\">----- Original Message ----<BR>From: Catherine PARPET &lt;CPARPET@DARROISVILLEY.COM&gt;<BR>To: jeeproject@yahoo.com<BR>Cc: Matthieu DE BOISSESON &lt;MDEBOISSESON@DARROISVILLEY.COM&gt;<BR>Sent: Tuesday, February 13, 2007 3:21:37 AM<BR>Subject: <BR><BR>\n<STYLE>\n<!--\n\n /* Style Definitions */\n p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{margin:0