</FONT><FONT color=black><SPAN lang=EN-GB style=\"COLOR: windowtext\">Ma\u00eetre</SPAN></FONT><FONT color=black><SPAN lang=EN-GB style=\"COLOR: windowtext\"> </SPAN></FONT><FONT color=black><SPAN lang=EN-GB style=\"COLOR: windowtext\">Chardon</SPAN></FONT><FONT color=black><SPAN lang=EN-GB style=\"COLOR: windowtext\">. We have tomorrow afternoon a meeting with the sellers\u2019 lawyer and notary. It is necessary that we have this document signed by you at the meeting.</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=black size=3><SPAN lang=EN-GB style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: windowtext\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=black size=3><SPAN lang=EN-GB style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: windowtext\">Kind regards,</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=black size=3><SPAN lang=EN-GB style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: windowtext\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=#003366 size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">Matthieu de BOISS\u00c9SON</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=black size=3><SPAN lang=EN-GB style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: windowtext\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P></DIV></DIV><BR></DIV></div><br>\n\n<hr size=1>Want to start your own business? Learn how on <a href=\"http://us.rd.yahoo.com/evt=41244/*http://smallbusiness.yahoo.com/r-index\">Yahoo! Small Business.</a></body></html>","is_from_epstein":true,"attachments":0,"avatar_color":"#9c27b0","stars":0,"is_redacted":false}]